  "keyFeatures": [
    "104 MCP tools covering issues, agents, approvals, goals, projects, routines, and more",
    "Stdio-based MCP server compatible with Claude Code, Cursor, VS Code, and Windsurf",
    "Automatic run-scoped JWT injection for all mutating requests via X-Paperclip-Run-Id",
    "Fail-fast startup validation of all required environment variables",
    "Docker/Podman support with a hardened Alpine-based image (0 OS-layer CVEs)",
    "Atomic issue checkout with expectedStatuses guard to prevent race conditions",
    "Two key types: agent key for autonomous ops, board key for destructive/approval operations",
    "Pre-built Claude Code skills for triage, epic closure, approvals audit, and release flow",
    "Structured error responses (isError: true) for all HTTP 4xx/5xx failures",
    "Compose stack for running the full Paperclip server + MCP server together"
  ],
